data.description:
4 Bedrooms, 2 baths, 2 car garage located in Tonkawa Village. Open Floor plan with Breakfast Bar between Kitchen and Living Area. Stainless steel Appliances. Corner Wood Burning Fireplace in the Living Area.  The Master Suite has a large  Walk-in Closet with a double Vanity, Garden Tub, and a separate Walk-in Shower. Split Bedroom Floor plan.
Covered Patio and an open Patio in the Back Yard. Wood Privacy fence with Sprinkler System.
Storage Shed and a Chicken Coop. Fenced garden Area with raised garden beds.
Check pictures for the Remodel list and upgrades Seller has done. Home is close to the Bypass for easy commute To Ft Hood, Shopping, or back way to Austin.
The seller would like to stay in the house until 1 May but could move out as early as 15 April.
